---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about REMODzz (Everquin, LLC) — premier remodeling and new home construction contractor serving Northern Illinois and Southern Wisconsin.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <span>About Us</span>
      </div>
      <h1>About <span class="text-primary">REMODzz</span></h1>
      <p>Premier remodeling and new home construction serving Northern Illinois and Southern Wisconsin.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="section bg-darker">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-images" data-animate>
          <img src="/images/portfolio/kitchen-libertyville-after.jpg" alt="REMODzz kitchen remodel" class="about-img-main" loading="lazy">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/addition-libertyville-after.jpg" alt="REMODzz addition project" class="about-img-secondary" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="about-content" data-animate>
          <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Building Trust, One Project at a Time</h2>
          <p>REMODzz (Everquin, LLC — formerly NeoTek Construction) is the premier remodeling and new home construction contractor serving Northern Illinois and Southern Wisconsin. We handle projects of all sizes, from a simple bathroom refresh or handyman task to a complex home addition, renovation, or complete redesign.</p>
          <p>Our in-house design services, exhaustively detailed proposals, and guaranteed schedules set us apart from the competition. We believe every client deserves to know exactly what their project entails, what it will cost, and when it will be complete.</p>
          <p>With experience in site-built, panelized, and modular construction, we bring versatile expertise to every project. Our team combines professional project management with skilled craftsmanship to deliver results that exceed expectations.</p>

          <div class="credential-grid">
            <div class="credential">
              <span class="credential-icon">✓</span>
              <span>Licensed & Insured</span>
            </div>
            <div class="credential">
              <span class="credential-icon">✓</span>
              <span>In-House Design</span>
            </div>
            <div class="credential">
              <span class="credential-icon">✓</span>
              <span>Energy Star Partner</span>
            </div>
            <div class="credential">
              <span class="credential-icon">✓</span>
              <span>2-Year Warranty</span>
            </div>
            <div class="credential">
              <span class="credential-icon">✓</span>
              <span>Habitat for Humanity</span>
            </div>
            <div class="credential">
              <span class="credential-icon">✓</span>
              <span>Guaranteed Schedules</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Advantages -->
  <section class="section bg-dark" id="advantages">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" data-animate>
        <span class="section-label">The REMODzz Difference</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Five Reasons We Stand Apart</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">95% of contractors don't offer our level of transparency, commitment, and quality. Here's what makes us different.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="advantages-grid">
        <div class="advantage-card" data-animate>
          <div class="advantage-header">
            <div class="advantage-num">1</div>
            <h3>Exhaustively Detailed Proposals</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Our proposals examine 54+ project categories so you know exactly what is and isn't covered. No surprises, no hidden costs, no budget overruns. You'll know precisely what your project entails before we break ground. Every material, every labor item, every finish — documented and priced.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="advantage-card" data-animate>
          <div class="advantage-header">
            <div class="advantage-num">2</div>
            <h3>In-House Design Services</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Professional design is included with every project. We provide custom layouts, detailed renderings, and visual views that ensure maximized functionality and visual appeal. See your project come to life before construction begins — this is critical for both budget accuracy and helping you visualize the finished product.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="advantage-card" data-animate>
          <div class="advantage-header">
            <div class="advantage-num">3</div>
            <h3>Guaranteed Schedules</h3>
          </div>
          <p>We provide a detailed calendar of events for every project, with specific penalties imposed on ourselves if completion dates are missed. Transparent communication about trades, schedules, and inspections throughout the entire process. You'll always know exactly where your project stands.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="advantage-card" data-animate>
          <div class="advantage-header">
            <div class="advantage-num">4</div>
            <h3>Custom Cabinetry</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Both in-house fabrication and trusted trade partnerships give you unlimited style, design, wood, and finish options at competitive pricing comparable to stock materials. Creative storage solutions are our specialty — we maximize every inch of your space.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="advantage-card" data-animate>
          <div class="advantage-header">
            <div class="advantage-num">5</div>
            <h3>Industry-Leading Two-Year Warranty</h3>
          </div>
          <p>We back our work with a comprehensive two-year warranty across all project types. This industry-leading protection gives you peace of mind long after the project is complete. If something isn't right, we make it right — period.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community -->
  <section class="section bg-darker">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="community-grid">
        <div data-animate>
          <span class="section-label">Community</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Giving Back</h2>
          <p>REMODzz is proud to be a Habitat for Humanity partner. We believe in using our skills to strengthen our community, one home at a time. Our charitable involvement in construction work reflects the same commitment to quality and care that we bring to every client project.</p>
          <p>As an Energy Star Partner, we're also committed to energy-efficient construction and environmentally conscious building practices. We help homeowners reduce their environmental footprint while lowering energy costs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="community-badges" data-animate>
          <div class="card">
            <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 12px;">❤️</div>
            <h4>Habitat for Humanity</h4>
            <p>Proud partner giving back through charitable construction work in our community.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 12px;">⚡</div>
            <h4>Energy Star Partner</h4>
            <p>Energy-efficient construction for an environmentally conscious approach.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-sm bg-dark">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 data-animate>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text); max-width: 500px; margin: 12px auto 28px;" data-animate>Contact us for a free, no-hassle estimate on your next project.</p>
      <div data-animate>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Free Estimate</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-images {
    position: relative;
  }
  .about-img-main {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .about-img-secondary {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30px;
    right: -20px;
    width: 55%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 4px solid var(--darker);
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .about-content p {
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .credential-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .credential {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .credential-icon {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .advantages-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .advantage-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 32px;
  }
  .advantage-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .advantage-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--darkest);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }
  .advantage-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .advantage-card p { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; }

  .community-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .community-grid p {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .community-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .community-badges h4 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .community-badges p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid,
    .community-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-img-secondary { position: static; width: 60%; margin-top: -40px; margin-left: auto; }
    .advantages-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
